Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.80,0:00:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前向前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.71,0:00:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯哦  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那邊  再過去點兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底往哪邊去啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.10,0:00:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  這邊喲這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.16,0:00:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我動手了  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.65,0:00:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.14,0:00:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  拿著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:48.04,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想被沖走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:00:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  昨天辛苦大家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.87,0:00:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.94,0:01:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.17,0:01:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是累得夠嗆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜健所賜  花了四小時才到海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.49,0:01:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們倒沒覺得怎麼樣  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.88,0:01:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過昨天夏奈才真夠嗆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暈車暈得這麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.26,0:01:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為自己不會暈車呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…健你個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差一點兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都那樣了還想游
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.99,0:01:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就是一隻想回歸大海的海龜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.70,0:01:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健那傢伙關鍵時刻就掉鏈子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想好好揍他一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:01:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為補償  我們不是聽你指揮把健叔埋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.92,0:02:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋了這呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  服了你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  健叔是你們的表哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.87,0:02:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.56,0:02:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼都好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺藤岡和千秋就像兄妹一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  不好說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄妹？這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.53,0:02:36.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田表現很反常哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:37.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會  不會  不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  千秋跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在找什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把藤岡放哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡是指千秋心愛的布娃娃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:02:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正這次又是你做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  快交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.98,0:03:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次可不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把它帶去海邊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是忘在那兒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是帶去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但沒從包裡拿出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我的確看到過藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海邊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還有其他人看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.25,0:03:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  這布娃娃千秋喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.44,0:03:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  每天都在用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.39,0:03:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有過這麼一番對話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  忘在海邊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在肯定已經被海水沖走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯放進我的行李裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在藤岡的行李裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡偷走藤岡打算做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒偷呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不記得有把它放進行李裡面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點兒呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別對著我的行李吐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿起來後就放在行李那邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說之後是被別人放進藤岡行李裡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  快點兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換衣服去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋把這東西都帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿她沒轍  忘了就麻煩了  幫她收起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此…是我放的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要是說出來應該會挨駡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.41,0:05:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈剛才你叫了聲  想起什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…愛你們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…那個嘛  能與你們相遇  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對優秀的你們表達一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要我們做出怎樣的反應？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想被沖走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到海的另一邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說春香  休息會兒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  讓我來教暑假作業的是你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  誰來了喲  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  夏奈  去開下門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶西瓜來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快看  是西瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡  多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉手之勞而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  過來下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好想吃西瓜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:08:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是剛吃過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.29,0:09:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天就應該吃西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜大人西瓜大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.66,0:09:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜會被你捂熱的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了勾引夏奈出的食誘招術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我可沒這麼想過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.89,0:09:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少裝了少裝了  都被我看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜如果不這麼切…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃西瓜的感覺就不一樣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.71,0:09:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這勺子  是夏奈一直用的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  我們比誰吃得快怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？  我可不會手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吐西瓜子的是夏奈嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  好髒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點兒都不髒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  一點兒都不卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:07.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（藤岡把這裡的「汚い」理解成了卑鄙）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好卑鄙  竟然抓住機會吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.18,0:10:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  這樣的舉止實在不雅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  被看到了嗎  真難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但說到舉止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡還在狼吞虎嚥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.77,0:10:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  好歹準備了勺子  給我用上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希  藤岡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事  南同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天吃完飯再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:37.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪次不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.93,0:10:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  下定決心今晚我來做咖喱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟春香在當真希的老師嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.39,0:10:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  要好好把佐料給藏起來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:05.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（隠し味：在料理中加入主要食材以外的材料（大多是微量）來進行烹調。\N這種方法多用於提鮮，也多作為料理店的秘方來使用。）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過多地加入佐料並不是正道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:13.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  別把胡蘿蔔藏起來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天佐料加入了胡蘿蔔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.78,0:11:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都讓你藏起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.16,0:11:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡蘿蔔好大個兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤岡  稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事  南同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人專用的勺子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放到我這邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.96,0:11:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致上客人和自家人的餐具是分開的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但勺子之類沒有細分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬  我們比誰吃得快怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.43,0:12:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連春香和夏奈都不在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田在幹嘛呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  今天幾號來著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8月31日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…阿珍暑假作業都做完了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  忘得一乾二淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.93,0:13:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.44,0:13:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想問千秋抄一下  但是被拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬馬也同樣被拒絕了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經打算放棄了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被老師責備啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  這事就交給我吧  內田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好提議？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試著和千秋談談
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓你能抄到作業
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你抄到了作業  讓我也抄一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.82,0:14:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…千秋能同意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.35,0:14:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:27.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:30.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋不想幫幫內田嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍經常來我家還以為你知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個夏天內田…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我家不是笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是哭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.61,0:14:56.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  我想再來一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.74,0:15:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來就是吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒想過要做什麼作業嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.18,0:15:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我喜歡被人依賴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但討厭被人當作救命稻草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說…說得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  既然這麼在意內田  你教她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說小學生水平的問題是小菜一碟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  千秋一直以為我是夏奈的後輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.81,0:15:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個國中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此就由我來教你做作業
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以做完讓我抄一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.99,0:15:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不對啊  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.74,0:15:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人插手小孩的作業…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.02,0:15:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍耳朵湊近些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是鐵石心腸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算等內田好好反省過後再給她看答案
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.25,0:16:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋說什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.69,0:16:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:20.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別全照抄  適當寫錯一兩處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…不  多虧了阿珍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:43.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（午間連續劇  終）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:46.42,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（電視購物）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,television  shoppin～g
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:46.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（此發音出自搞笑藝人エド·はるみ）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  進展很順利嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:16:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我也抄一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不勞而獲  你想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  真小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事  冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說真  作業做完的話就讓我抄一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是回答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不到夏天的風
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是秋天了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要換秋裝穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  為了對逝去的夏天表示惋惜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後再穿一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞了半天是泳衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別穿好了再吐槽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要在浴室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿著泳衣你還想去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是秋天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭秋天  夏天再久一點兒多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年夏天實在太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.12,0:20:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的某日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被華麗地吐了西瓜子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是夏天的某日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.95,0:20:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛麵汁被放進了芥末
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後還是夏天的某日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是可樂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫吃了醬油味的刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個令人討厭的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.74,0:20:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把夏天還我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  晚飯做什麼好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我家燒的栗子飯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.89,0:21:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚店老闆給了我秋刀魚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這魚真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對魚店老闆用了什麼花招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是夏樹叫我帶來你們家的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.27,0:21:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\fsp56}　{\fsp1}eryngii{\fsp1}{\r}\N好奇怪的杏鮑菇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是松茸大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.73,0:21:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨  冬馬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.52,0:21:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們輸了  冬馬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.22,0:21:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.43,0:21:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逝去的夏天…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起不少事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好好期待今天的晚飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.19,0:22:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有快去換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.96,0:22:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.98,0:22:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松茸大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.84,0:22:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋天最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.70,0:22:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.87,0:22:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.39,0:22:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這栗子飯怎麼不見栗子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.08,0:22:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真是意外
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這兒有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.97,0:22:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的也有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.68,0:22:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道埋在裡面了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.56,0:22:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.11,0:22:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這盤子裡怎麼只剩下蘿蔔泥了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.04,0:22:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會這秋刀魚太新鮮跳起來逃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:56.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:22:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松茸大人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.37,0:23:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松茸大人也不見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.10,0:23:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松茸大人到底去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.17,0:23:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松茸這東西  外行人輕易是找不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.90,0:23:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看了秋天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.15,0:23:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.83,0:23:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快樂的時間總是轉瞬即逝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.27,0:23:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒玩盡興嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一回  南家三姐妹～歡迎回來～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.33,0:23:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.59,0:23:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是屬於我的季節  蠢貨
